RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: (NODE = GLOBAL.NODE OR GLOBAL.NODE = (SELECT R.HOST_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH R,OLTMS_BANK B WHERE B.HO_BRANCH = R.BRANCH_CODE)) AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE HOST_NAME = NODE AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A')
BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND MSG_STATUS = 'N' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND DIRECTIVE_STATUS = 'B'

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_BG_STATUS.SEQ_NO = MSTBS_BG_STATUS__AL.SEQ_NO AND OLTBS_BG_STATUS.NODE = MSTBS_BG_STATUS__AL.NODE AND OLTBS_BG_STATUS.PROCESS = MSTBS_BG_STATUS__AL.PROCESS
